{"type": "article", "id": 24452, "title": "带蓝色气泡的花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-25T07:00:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 81, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607102431CuKhmcnL0tGAHNeo.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组陶瓷花瓶来自荷兰两个年轻人，花瓶的形状很普通却有气泡一样的蓝色花纹。他们创造了一种特殊的上釉方式得以将肥皂泡的自然状态印在花瓶上，可以看到颜色深浅和形状大小都不均匀的图案，都有些偶然和随机，看起来很自然。它打破传统花瓶图案的精致和程式化，也很特别。<a href=\"http://www.oddness.nl/index.html\">这里是工作室链接</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607102429NZVTL4HcbCkGYMvt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607102429gVa3ToNhJwxHAlBq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607102430avY8OB75QyrJMIXU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607102430RBPvNTSWn9uydVKf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060710243018sOMdvmxU7aH49b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}